column11:
  In this paper, we study the existence of infinitely many periodic solutions
for second order Hamiltonian systems $\ddot{u}+\nabla_u V(t,u)=0$, where $V(t,
u)$ is either asymptotically quadratic or superquadratic as $|u|\to \infty$.

